description.narrative:
The proposed intervention has the following objectives:
> to advance understanding of the role and the link between the illicit economy and the crisis in Mali, on the part of key stakeholders in the peace agreement implementation; 
> to share lessons from the region on drug control and drug trafficking policy  > to share emerging policy recommendations from the field of peace research on ‘decriminalizing peace’, and addressing organised crime through a development lens;
> to gain a greater understanding of the Malian government's capacity to tackle organised crime.
